'''Secrets''' in Final Fantasy IV include hidden items, rare encounters, and optional content.

== Hidden Items ==

=== Adamant Armor ===
The best armor in the game, hidden in a complex sidequest.

'''How to Obtain:'''
# Obtain the Pink Tail from Princess Flan in the Lunar Subterrane
# Trade the Pink Tail to the Tail Collector in Adamant Isle Grotto
# Receive the Adamant Armor

'''Notes:'''
* Pink Tail drop rate is extremely rare (1/64)
* Princess Flans appear in specific rooms only
* Adamant Armor provides the highest defense

