'''Location:'''
* Sealed Cave, in a hidden passage
* Requires searching specific walls

=== Masamune ===
An early powerful weapon for Palom (temporarily).

'''Location:'''
* Found in the Antlion's Den
* In a hidden passage near the Ant Lion boss room

