== Optional Content ==

=== Land of Summons ===
While required for story, contains optional treasures:
* Hidden paths with rare items
* Challenging enemy encounters
* Asura and Leviatan as optional summons

=== Sylph Cave ===
Optional dungeon with helpful summon:
* Retrieve Yang's frying pan from his wife
* Use it to wake Yang
* Obtain Sylph summon

== Tips ==

